A cyberpunk cityscape of Mumbai at night, featuring towering corporate skyscrapers with glowing neon circuitry patterns running up their facades like digital veins. In the foreground, a massive holographic portal gateway shimmers between two buildings, casting electric blue and magenta light across the rain-slicked streets below. Silhouettes of ambitious professionals walk toward the portal, their reflections creating ripples in shallow puddles. Flying vehicles streak across the dark purple sky between buildings adorned with holographic advertisements. The architecture blends traditional Indian design elements with futuristic chrome and glass structures. Dense fog rolls through the lower streets while the upper levels gleam with technological advancement. The overall mood is energetic, aspirational, and full of opportunity, suggesting a gateway to new possibilities in a high-tech future.
